ShopClues board has backed Co-founders Radhika Aggarwal and Sanjay Sethi in the ongoing battle between the third Co-founder Sandeep Aggarwal against the two. "We're proud of the fantastic progress made by the ShopClues team under Radhika and Sanjay's leadership," said a ShopClues board statement. "It's disappointing to see an ex-founder engaged in personal vendetta on a public forum," it added.